version_description: As Barry Gibb plays it, in open D tuning, chord legend and info on tuning included.
Played on clean electric guitar with chorus,strummed with rhythm and muted action,very easy to play and jam to.You can also play Em Em7 Em6 Em on the verse Em to add a little rhythm.
No offence intended to previous contributors but this version includes all lyrics and chords to the outro lyrics.
